{
  "texts": [
    "RPN network is an outstanding representative of convolutional neural networks in deep learning object classification algorithms.",
    "Experimental results show that it improves the detection efficiency.Reference [40] achieved vehicle object detection by continuously increasing the size and scale of anchors through adjustments to hyperparameters in the Faster R-CNN algorithm.",
    "Reference [41] proposed using Resnet101 as a backbone network in Faster R-CNN and combining it with Neural Architecture Search (NAS) to generate optimal cross-layer connections for more efficient extraction of multilevel features.",
    "In addition, they used an object feature enrichment technique that combines multilevel feature information with contextual information from the last layer after connecting across layers.",
    "They obtained the final RoI features through cascading, scaling, and dimensionality reduction to enrich the vehicle object information."
  ]
}